Name: button menu

Synonyms: button menu, button contents menu, menu button

Type: glossary

Description:
A <menu> built from the contents of a <button>, and displayed when the
<button> is clicked.

Button menus can be displayed as pulldown or <popup menu|popup menus>,
<combo box|combo boxes>, or <tabbed button|dialog tabs>.

References: tabbed button (glossary), combo box (glossary),
popup menu (glossary), menu (glossary), button (glossary)

Tags: menus

